Blackheart let out a sigh. "Yes indeed old man, that I am. One more time I 
must suffer your precense." They bickered like old bots but in the end 
Blackheart would go into the very pits with that old warrior. It was one of 
the few predacons he had respect for. The tohers were...most..of the bots on 
this ship."
